Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do this to elderly\Npeople... But you're important witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if\Nyou died or ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The back entrance and\Nmost of the windows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have been barricaded\Nwith furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone really wanted to,\Nthey could easily break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than nothing.\NLet's go to the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if something\Nwere to happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to survive and\Ntell the world the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim, stay in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If something\Nhappens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. There's no need to worry.\NA strong ally is coming to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes to save us\Nwhenever we're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He never let's evil go unpunished.\NHe's the Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the path through\Nthe woods to the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure most of\Nthe children have escaped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You go quickly, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't looked around\Nthe center of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me.\NYou lead everyone to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. There's just one thing\NI'd like to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Bonaparta.. .\Nno.. .Klaus Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. He's the owner\Nof the Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. I'm on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away in a panic.\NBut the town is full of corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where\NI should run to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's giving orders\Nfrom his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange that he kept\Ncoming and going from his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time, he'd change\Nhis clothes and take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A room on the fourth floor\Nof the Hotel Bergbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I ...didn't know he was\Nthat sort of person. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Everyone's hiding\Nin Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get there\Nby yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By myself? I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My journey into delusion...\Nhas finally become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence of you marks the end of\Nfollowing what I thought were delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My duty as a police officer\Nbegins from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally going back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this girl to the Hotel Versteck.\NThe person you're after is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz.. .Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge,\Nwhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?\NTo work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There're a lot of things\NI want to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your deepest memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want to remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This memory... Johan.. .\NIf Johan remembers this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm from this town.\NDon't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's is the man\Nwho's giving you orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "Where's Roberto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up. Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore.\NThere are dead bodies everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go crazy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we've got to get to\NHotel Versteck as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately. ..\NYour wife is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side. It's dangerous here.\NGet to somewhere safe immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your gun ! I'm going to\Ngun down the guy who shot Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the gun right now!\NHe destroyed our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife.. .\Nwouldn't want you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife wants that child to be safe.\NAm I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to a path through the\Nwoods to the north, where you can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go towards the path\Ninstead of the hotel as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll be right back.\NDon't move from this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... They're really not after\Nthe lottery prize we won, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. I didn't feel like I was living\Nfor the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There really was\Nsomething wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that money,\NI ended up buying a bunch of guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal's what's best of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to let my wife know\Nthat we're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you hear me, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Henich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Henich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're shooting at us from\Nthe building across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this hotel\Nhave a basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a storehouse\Nunder the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How are your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is going crazy because\Nhe can't get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No he's not, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's... Just like when he\Nhits me every day, Dad's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that your dad is the sort\Nof person to do this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This will end if I go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat it.\NI won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tie you down here\Nif you keep saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here. I'll deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When things get tough,\Nthe Magnificent Steiner will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen cases like that\Nduring my experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By imposing an excessive amount\Nof stress from anger or sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a child will manifest\Na different personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children were\Nexceptionally violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them\Ncommitted suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you've lived\Nas long as you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. I'm unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I have to say,\Neven for just a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?\NWho gave you your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you're people\Nfrom the old East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're former\Nsecret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nobody from nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. Don't just follow orders,\Nbut think with your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Think with your heart\Nabout what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!\NI came all this way by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Magnificent Steiner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched it so fervently each day,\Nsitting so close to the TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no memory of\Nwatching the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Call out my name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on. Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if the main character,\Nthe weak young man,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}realized that he turned into the\NMagnificent Steiner when he got angry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if that young man\Nfound happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That young man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That young man\Nbecomes happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little further and\Nwe'll be out of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Ruhenheim,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happening\Nin the town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People came into\Nthe town with weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in town began\Nkilling each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NWe're on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see an Asian man...\Na Japanese man with long hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. He was desperately trying\Nto help these children get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's staying in\Nthe town trying to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When we split up,\Nhe mentioned the Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my car right outside\Nthe path through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that car to transport\Nthe injured and the sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And contact the police\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you planning on\Ngoing to the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that.\NYou'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's...\Nthat Asian man is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save him.\NContact the police immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel Versteck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I knew you'd come,\NDr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Two in the neighboring building...\None on the floor below this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a total of four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magnificent Steiner appeared,\Ndidn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it on my own.\NI did it in a fit of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, those wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's a letter.\NI got it from Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He found it in\Nthe Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Help him. He headed to\Nthe Hotel Bergbach by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I do that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me rest.. .for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is. ..Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been raining a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This area is nice when it's sunny. ..\Ndon't you think, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When it gets sunny again,\Nlet's have a picnic with Wim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have good wine...\Nand good cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad\Nbecause I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,\NI'm sad because my son died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make\Npeople's feelings go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotions were\Nlost somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if I had received a letter that\Nhad been sent to me decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is true sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The last episode of\NThe Magnificent Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably turned back\Ninto a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
